    "answer_id" : 50941562,
    "question_id" : 45615474,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Make sure your Gradle version is <code>3.*.*</code> or higher before using &quot;implementation&quot;.</p>\n<p>Open the project level Gradle file under dependencies:</p>\n<pre><code>dependencies{\n    classpath 'com.android.tools.build:gradle:3.1.2'\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Open the 'gradle-wrapper.properties' file and set the <code>distributionUrl</code>:</p>\n<pre><code>distributionUrl=https\\://services.gradle.org/distributions/gradle-4.4-all.zip\n</code></pre>\n<p>or latest version.</p>\n<p>Sync the project. I Hope this solves your problem.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
