      "post_id" : 51129790,
      "comment_id" : 116256344,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Thanks!  This is the only suggestion that actually worked for me.  I was using compile and the project actually compiled, but then the classes on the AAR were not available at runtime inside the app.   This form of implementation solved both problems."
    } ],
