    "answer_id" : 51129790,
    "question_id" : 45615474,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Your Code   </p>\n\n<pre><code>dependencies {\n    compile fileTree(include: ['*.jar'], dir: 'libs')\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Replace it By </p>\n\n<pre><code>dependencies {\nimplementation fileTree(include: ['*.jar'], dir: 'libs')\n</code></pre>\n"
