    "answer_id" : 55237854,
    "question_id" : 45615474,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>So ridiculous, but I still wanna share my experience in case of that someone falls into the situation like me.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Please check if you changed: <code>compileSdkVersion</code> --> <code>implementationSdkVersion</code> by mistake</strong></p>\n"
