    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1567143144,
    "creation_date" : 1567143144,
    "answer_id" : 57720971,
    "question_id" : 45615474,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As mentioned here, <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/50941562/2186220\">https://stackoverflow.com/a/50941562/2186220</a>, use gradle plugin version 3 or higher while using 'implementation'.</p>\n\n<p>Also, use the <code>google()</code> repository in <code>buildscript</code>.</p>\n\n<pre><code>buildscript {\n    repositories {\n        google()\n    }\n    dependencies {\n        classpath 'com.android.tools.build:gradle:3.1.2'\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>These changes should solve the issue.</p>\n"
  }, {
