    "question_id" : 45615474,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As suggested in official <a href=\"https://developer.android.com/studio/releases/gradle-plugin?gclid=Cj0KCQjw--GFBhDeARIsACH_kdYZ1UTjSCJ4LtZ46Zq1f_gHAcsHqvPQfbwo7kc8FM2UNGifODV_2EYaAtkpEALw_wcB&amp;gclsrc=aw.ds\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">docs</a> you need add these :</p>\n<pre><code>buildscript {\n    repositories {\n        // Gradle 4.1 and higher include support for Google's Maven repo using\n        // the google() method. And you need to include this repo to download\n        // Android Gradle plugin 3.0.0 or higher.\n        google()\n        ...\n    }\n    dependencies {\n        classpath 'com.android.tools.build:gradle:4.2.0'\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>adding these remove my error. Also use implementation instead of compile.</p>\n"
