    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Solved this by adding my dependancies in the app folder</p>\n<p>Go to: <strong>app -&gt; Gradle Scripts -&gt; gradle.build(Module: app) and add</strong> the dependencies in that file and not the global build.gradle file</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/su2E7.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/su2E7.png\" alt=\"Add your dependency in app/build.gradle\" /></a></p>\n"
