    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For me the problem was that I wrote:</p>\n<pre><code>android {\n    compileSdk 31\n…\n</code></pre>\n<p>Instead of:</p>\n<pre><code>android {\n    compileSdkVersion 31\n</code></pre>\n<p>So make sure your <code>build.gradle</code> is correct.</p>\n"
